name: XTZ F90 ///M5
description:
A highly detailed virtual representation and appreciation of a 2018 Stage 2 built F90 M5 - The original vehicle was built for a close friend who has helped me out in unimaginable ways and also introduced me to Tezos platform.

This highly detailed vector drawing includes a total of 511 Hidden and exposed Tezos logos throughout the vehicle.

It's a fusion of appreciation and introduction to XTZ and also the start to my NFT Journey.

Vehicle details.
2018 Snapper Rocks blue F90 M5 with Manhart Stage 2 tune, Manhart Downpipes, Akrapovic exhaust, Eventuri intake and a full AC Schnitzer kit.

Unfortunately this vehicle does not exist anymore, but this art shall live on!
